description: Move a dedicated IP address to an existing dedicated IP pool.

parameters.name: Ip
parameters.description: The IP address that you want to move to the dedicated IP pool. The value you specify has to be a dedicated IP address that's associated with your Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: DestinationPoolName
parameters.description: The name of the IP pool that you want to add the dedicated IP address to. You have to specify an IP pool that already exists.
